<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Jared Leto recently confirmed he will play iconic artist Andy Warhol in an upcoming biopic. </p>

<p>But the 48-year-old actor didn't seem to be back to work just yet as he enjoyed a day out with girlfriend Valery Kaufman, 26. </p>

<p>The two were spotted heading to a rock climbing gym in Los Angeles on Tuesday. </p>

